Change Log
============================================================

Version 1.1.1 - Minor fixes and features
------------------------------------------------------------
2011-11-17

* Added previous/next to the paging controls

* Added SetError on an element
    > SetError([message]) will add a message to the element
      and apply custom styling to highlight the element. 
* Added map format control
    > Calling SetFormat('coordinates') will turn co-ordinates
      in a grid into a link to Google Maps
      
* Added HTML element
    > Can add custom HTML as an element
    
* Added render-mode to rows. Rows can be rendered as either:
    > Builder_Form::RENDER_MODE_INPUT_ONLY
    > Builder_Form::RENDER_MODE_LABEL_INPUT

* Added some Builder Helper constants (rather than using text
values in parameter passing) 

* Updated examples to use the new elements and format controls


Version 1.1 - Initial Release
------------------------------------------------------------
* Initial release